In [3]:
def data_preproc(df):
    df.dropna(inplace=True)
    df.drop(['point.id', 'motherset', 'origin'], axis=1, inplace=True)
    label = pd.get_dummies(df['original.label'], prefix='original.label')
    df.drop('original.label', inplace=True, axis=1)
    df = pd.concat((df, label), axis=1)
    X = df.drop('ground.truth', axis=1)
    df['ground.truth'] = df['ground.truth'].map({'nominal': 0, 'anomaly': 1})
    Y = df['ground.truth']
    return X, Y

2. 采用相同评价标准进行比较¶

3. 结果可视化分析¶

In [6]:
def train_and_analyse(X, Y):
    models = {'KNN' : KNN(), 'LOF' : LOF(), 'PCA' : PCA(), 'ABOD' : ABOD(n_neighbors=10), 'HBOS' : HBOS(), 'OCSVM' : OCSVM()}
    tsne_X = TSNE().fit_transform(X)
    plt.scatter(tsne_X[:, 0], tsne_X[:, 1], c=Y)
    plt.title('ground_truth')
    plt.show()
    for n, m in models.items():
        m.fit(X)
        predictions = m.predict(X)
        scores = m.decision_scores_
        print(n + ': ')
        print('roc_auc_score: ', roc_auc_score(Y, scores))
        print('accuracy_score: ', accuracy_score(Y, predictions))
        print('f1_score: ', f1_score(Y, predictions))
        plt.scatter(tsne_X[:, 0], tsne_X[:, 1], c=predictions)
        plt.title(n + ': ')
        plt.show()

path = "benchmarks"
files_list = os.listdir(path)
for file in files_list:
    df = pd.read_csv(path + '/' + file)
    X, Y = data_preproc(df)
    train_and_analyse(X, Y)
